textAfterTable: 16 Songs Biography Formed: Miami, FL Genre: Hip-Hop/Rap Years Active: '80s, '90s Gucci Crew was one of the most prolific and crucial Miami booty-bass groups during the '80s and early '90s; when all was said and done, they had released five studio albums and one compilation. Each studio album was released on the group's own label. They debuted with a self-titled album in 1983 and followed it with 1989's What Time Is It?
